OL,3,CSri Lanka takes custody of Iranian
OL,4,Cship days after US sinks warship
OL,6,FSri Lanka has brought more than 200
OL,7,Fsailors ashore from an Iranian ship
OL,8,Fafter one of its engines failed, days
OL,9,Fafter the US sank an Iranian warship
OL,10,Fin the Indian Ocean.
OL,12,FThe 204 sailors of the IRIS Bushehr
OL,13,Fhave been brought to the Welisara
OL,14,FNaval Base near the capital, Colombo.
OL,15,FAround 15 others remain onboard, with
OL,16,FSri Lankan naval personnel for
OL,17,Fassistance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
