OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772838681
OL,3,CSri Lanka takes custody of Iranian
OL,4,Cship days after US sinks warship
OL,6,FIt is the second time in as many days
OL,7,Fthat Sri Lanka been dragged into the
OL,8,Ffallout from the conflict between the
OL,9,FUS, Israel, and Iran. On Wednesday,
OL,10,Fthe US sank the IRIS Dena off Sri
OL,11,FLanka's coast, as it made its way back
OL,12,Ffrom naval exercises where it had been
OL,13,Fparticipating alongside more than 70
OL,14,Fother countries, including the US.
OL,16,FThe Sri Lankan navy said it had
OL,17,Frecovered 87 bodies and rescued 32
OL,18,Fpeople from the sinking ship.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
