OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772838681
OL,3,CSri Lanka takes custody of Iranian
OL,4,Cship days after US sinks warship
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe Sri Lankan navy rescued 32 sailors
OL,12,Fand recovered 87 bodies from the Dena.
OL,14,FSri Lanka's retired former foreign
OL,15,Fsecretary said the country had acted
OL,16,Fresponsibly and impartially by
OL,17,Fresponding to the Bushehr's distress
OL,18,Fcall on Thursday evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
