FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772838681
OL,3,CSri Lanka takes custody of Iranian
OL,4,Cship days after US sinks warship
OL,6,F"Sri Lanka, as a party to the Law of
OL,7,FSea and The Hague Convention, had no
OL,8,Foption but to do what it did by
OL,9,Fmounting a humanitarian operation to
OL,10,Fprovide assistance to save lives and
OL,11,Fprovide medical care to the affected,"
OL,12,FH.M.G.S. Palihakkara said.
OL,14,F"You could not have ignored the
OL,15,Fdistress call. Even the attacking
OL,16,Fpowers cannot leave shipwrecked
OL,17,Fsailors dying. That is the law,"
OL,18,FPalihakkara said.
