PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772838681
OL,3,CSri Lanka takes custody of Iranian
OL,4,Cship days after US sinks warship
OL,6,FIranian sailors onboard the ship have
OL,7,Fbeen interpreting operational
OL,8,Finstructions, manuals and logs for
OL,9,Ftheir Sri Lankan counterparts, and it
OL,10,Fwill be taken to the port of
OL,11,FTrincomalee in the east of the
OL,12,Fcountry, he said.
OL,14,FSri Lankan President Anura Kumara
OL,15,FDissanayake said authorities had
OL,16,Fdecided to take control of the Bushehr
OL,17,Fafter discussions with Iranian
OL,18,Fofficials and the ship's captain about
OL,19,Fthe engine failure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
