PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772838681
OL,3,CSri Lanka takes custody of Iranian
OL,4,Cship days after US sinks warship
OL,6,F"We have to understand that this is
OL,7,Fnot an ordinary situation. It's a
OL,8,Frequest by a ship belonging to one
OL,9,Fparty to enter into our port," he told
OL,10,Fjournalists.
OL,12,F"We have to consider that according to
OL,13,Fthe international treaties and
OL,14,Fconventions."
OL,16,FSri Lanka was guided by neutrality
OL,17,Fwhile seeking to uphold humanitarian
OL,18,Fprinciples, Dissanayake added.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
