OL,3,CSri Lanka takes custody of Iranian
OL,4,Cship days after US sinks warship
OL,6,FHe posted on X on Friday: "No civilian
OL,7,Fshould die in wars. Our approach is
OL,8,Fthat every single life is as precious
OL,9,Fas our own."
OL,11,FIran's Foreign Minister Abbas Araghchi
OL,12,Fsaid the Dena had been carrying
OL,13,F"almost 130" members of crew when it
OL,14,Fwas attacked, calling the sinking an
OL,15,F"atrocity at sea".
OL,17,F"The US will come to bitterly regret
OL,18,Fthe precedent it has set," Araghchi
OL,19,Fwrote on social media.
